<P>
   REAL-STYLE15 _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ There is no Ann Taylor.
Ann Taylor is a name chosen for its marketing value alone. An
All-American name. ``Taylor'' for tailoring. It beats Mimi
Lieberskin or Richard Lieberskin, the names of the husband-and-wife
team that created the company in 1954. Now Patti DeRosa runs the
company. Age 45, size 6. She started in sales. Like other women in
the office, DeRosa test-drives new clothing ideas. Wears them,
washes them. (EDS: Part one in a series _ part two moved Tuesday.)
(Anna, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
