<P>
   FRAMPTON-ALIVE _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ If there were a test to
determine whether you're a rock has-been, Peter Frampton would pass
with flying colors. Appeared on an album of children's songs?
Check. Moved to Nashville? Check. Started going bald? Check. Things
have changed for the 48-year-old rock legend. Frampton survived the
Disco Decade, but not without watching his glory days pass by. But
say this for the once shaggy-haired guitarist: He's got a sense of
humor about it. (Passy, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
