   CAMPAIGN-POLL (Washington) _ With three weeks to go before the
midterm elections, support for the Republican Congress has eroded
significantly in the aftermath of the House vote to open a formal
impeachment inquiry, according to the latest New York Times/CBS
News Poll. By Alison Mitchell.
</P>
