   OLY-BOMBING (Washington) _ With the trail of Eric Robert Rudolph
turning cold in the mountainous wilds of North Carolina, federal
law enforcement officials announced Wednesday that he had been
formally charged with the Centennial Olympic Park bombing and two
other Atlanta bomb attacks in 1996. By David Johnston.
</P>
